**Summarizing class count and pattern evaluation approach**

I've identified 37 total concrete classes across domain, services, controllers, and repository, with no interfaces or abstract classes present. I'll document patterns found—Controller, Service Layer, Repository—with 7 pattern-involved classes, yielding a pattern density of 0.19, and write a markdown table summarizing components, types, patterns, and notes along with an overall SOLID/decoupling grade.
